{"tid":444896,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[點解無人睇]《Only the brave 烈焰雄心》 討論區","createTime":"2017-10-23T01:44:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-07T13:56:24.000Z","uid":31773,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"881e7e088a9b9bcf31396559aa0cf21b94fb58a3","tid":444896,"uid":31773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T01:44:01.000Z","msg":"明明一套有頗有水準既電影<br />\n<br />\n但入場人數零丁<br />\n<br />\n希望可以推到畀更多人睇<br />\n<br />\n先非劇透講下，套戲雖然頗長成130分鐘<br />\n<br />\n但130分鐘用黎建構成班角色既關係、情感，成隊畀觀眾既觀感，係絕對有需要的，換來成套戲最尾個幕係值得，我最後真係睇到呆左(希望大家唔好劇透呢個位)<br />\n<br />\n再者成套戲個種手足情深，男人既浪漫真係好正，成個院真係聽到唔少馬尿聲<br />\n<br />\n而運鏡，特效，音樂都係唔錯，絕對值得入場支持"},{"pid":"e19f610f4852856392c01374cbc2fa1e4c5a2ea1","tid":444896,"uid":5905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T01:47:19.000Z","msg":"睇完<br />\n唔錯"},{"pid":"57e1ce63f29403dea77ddf70cfb68ac80f9d35f6","tid":444896,"uid":31773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T01:50:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇完<br />\n唔錯</blockquote><br />\n我初頭都畀trailer呃左，<br />\n以為會仗，點知喜出望外"},{"pid":"dbc4b717858fafdfa7fa70151a00aa8913a3af93","tid":444896,"uid":35556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T02:22:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c688f187bddd63c7e15297cf5c7f3674633c22b2","tid":444896,"uid":31773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T02:40:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"520c04d87b22934689f85f14f031e6020a1ea527","tid":444896,"uid":20890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T15:47:15.000Z","msg":"睇左 好撚正"},{"pid":"0918b4e0c9710acbaae1e705d17a046067aec985","tid":444896,"uid":14703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T16:23:08.000Z","msg":"好耐無試過係戲院睇到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最尾真係好正<br />\n最尾十分鐘收得好靚<br />\n個節奏亦